// Template chooser for new node main entry.
//
// Prefer one of these templates:
// 1) main.simple.cpp.example
//    - Use when node setup has no long-lived runtime-owned state.
//
// 2) main.with_context.cpp.example
//    - Use when setup needs runtime-owned state (timers/codecs/bridges/etc.).
//
// Both templates use:
// - node::entry::RunSimpleNodeMain...
// - SimpleNode auto thread observability
// - unified Kafka handler registration pattern
